# Section 9 — Long-Term Vision

Title

Built for solar first

Solar Sanchalak is the first product in a broader vision to digitize field-service maintenance workflows.

The platform architecture is designed to support additional infrastructure maintenance domains in the future.

However, the current focus remains solar operations and maintenance.

